KidsRuby Installer for OSX

This installer is based on Platypus (http://www.sveinbjorn.org/platypus)

Get all needed resources to build an installer by running install.sh

The script installer.sh is what Platypus uses for the installation process on an end-user computer

# OSX installer build
QT
- build qt 4.7.3 universal darwin libs for OSX. If using homebrew that means:
  brew install qt --universal
  
- copy target files to installer resources dir
  /usr/local/Cellar/qt/4.7.3

qtbindings gem
- build universal binary for OSX using qt 4.7.3 libs
- copy .gem file to installer resources dir

